<p>
You can help protect the planet by:
</p>

<ul>
<li>Use reusable water bottles to reduce single-use plastic and minimize pollution.</li>
<li> Use reusable water bottles to reduce single-use plastic and minimize pollution.</li>
<li>Reduce waste by recycling, composting, and choosing products with minimal packaging.</li>
<li>Plant trees to restore ecosystems, improve air quality, and combat climate change.</li>
<li>Participate in clean-up events to keep your community, parks, and waterways free from litter.</li>
<li>Spread environmental awareness by sharing knowledge, campaigns, and eco-friendly practices with friends and family.</li>
<li>Support sustainable businesses that prioritize ethical production, renewable energy, and environmentally friendly materials.</li>
<li>Educate others about climate change and the importance of protecting biodiversity, forests, and oceans.</li>
</ul>

